text: CS Progresul Șomcuta Mare is a Romanian football club based in Șomcuta Mare, Maramureș County which plays in Liga IV. == History == Progresul Șomcuta Mare played mostly in the Fourth tier and played 5 seasons in Liga III and won promotion in 2020 against Sportul Șimleu Silvaniei. In 2022 the club relegated back in the fourth league finishing 9th place. Category:Romanian football clubs
title: CS Progresul Șomcuta Mare
